<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Microblog</title>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.js" integrity="sha256-H+K7U5CnXl1h5ywQfKtSj8PCmoN9aaq30gDh27Xc0jk=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/style/index.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/public/logic/index.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="page">

      <div id="page1">
        <h1>Benvenuto nel microblog di Karim Bachir!</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>Scegli cosa fare:</p>
        <div id="action">
          <a onclick="triggerLoginForm()"><i class="bi bi-door-open-fill"></i> Accedi</a>
          <a onclick="triggerSigninForm()"><i class="bi bi-person-plus-fill"></i> Registrati</a>
          <a href="/microblog/guest"><i class="bi bi-person"></i> Accedi come guest</a>
        </div>
        <p>Se ti registrerai avrai la possibilità di pubblicare post, commentare e mettere like ai post che ti piaceranno.</p>
        <p>Se invece deciderai di non registrarti avrai comunque la possibilità di visualizzare i post degli utenti registrati e i relativi commenti ma non potrai crearne di nuovi e non potrai commentare o mettere like.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="page2">
        <div id="login">
          <h3>Compila i campi:</h3>
          <label for="loginUsername">username/email</label>
          <input type="text" name="username" id="loginUsername" value="">
          <br>
          <label for="loginPassword">password</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" id="loginPassword" value="">
          <br>
          <button type="submit" name="login" id="loginButton">Login</button>
        </div>
        <div id="signin">
          <h3>Compila i campi:</h3>
          <label for="name">name</label>
          <input type="text" name="name" id="name" value=""><br>

          <label for="surname">surname</label>
          <input type="text" name="surname" id="surname" value=""><br>

          <label for="email">email</label>
          <input type="text" name="email" id="email" value=""><br>

          <label for="dateOfBirth">dateOfBirth</label>
          <input type="text" name="dateOfBirth" id="dateOfBirth" value=""><br>

          <label for="signinUsername">username/email</label>
          <input type="text" name="username" id="signinUsername" value=""><br>

          <label for="signinPassword">password</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" id="signinPassword" value=""><br>

          <button type="submit" name="signIn" id="signInButton">signIn</button>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="status">
          <p> <%= status %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <h5>PWM Microblog</h5>
      <h5>2020/2021</h5>
      <h5>Karim Bachir</h5>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>